{"tid":1509452,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人臉辨識曠視科技申請在港上市","createTime":"2019-08-27T00:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T02:02:52.000Z","uid":146803,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec786e0e9e3c12055339852bc0c33755525b72f","tid":1509452,"uid":146803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:21:16.000Z","msg":"曠視科技的技術主要採用深度學習跨亞軍，透過將電腦視覺技術商業化，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將人臉辨識技術應用於個人設備、城市和供應鏈三大物聯網領域中</span></span></strong>。這獨角獸公司去年收入達 14.27 億人民幣，據報告指達到中國雲端人臉辨識身份驗證解決方案產業超過 60%，不過<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同年虧損 33.52 億人民幣，並且逐年增加中。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/unwire.pro/2019/08/26/chinese-ai-megvii-hk-ipo/ai/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Funwire.pro%2F2019%2F08%2F26%2Fchinese-ai-megvii-hk-ipo%2Fai%2Famp%2F&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=bb96e3cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/unwire.pro/2019/08/26/chinese-ai-megvii-hk-ipo/ai/amp/</a>"},{"pid":"bdc7d9a503d19d329f2f209e840faa5cf7e98a16","tid":1509452,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=d1745886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=b8740d2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_bla